@startuml
title Check Order Status Sequence Diagram

actor Customer
participant "WhatsApp Bot\n(src/bot.js)" as Bot
participant "Order Helpers\n(src/botHelpers.js)" as Helpers
participant "Orders Store\n(src/orders.js)" as Orders

Customer -> Bot : Select Get Order Status
Bot -> Helpers : sendOrderStatusList(userId)
Helpers -> Orders : getOrdersForUser(phone)
Orders --> Helpers : matching orders
Helpers --> Bot : formatted order-status list
Bot --> Customer : Show current order statuses

@enduml
